[
  {
    "start": 0.0,
    "text": "I feel like I'm back in Seoul."
  },
  {
    "start": 6.4,
    "text": "Korean food is taking over America and this restaurant, Kisachikdang, specifically has"
  },
  {
    "start": 12.9,
    "text": "gone completely viral."
  },
  {
    "start": 15.2,
    "text": "Personally, I love Kisachikdang and go often in Seoul because the meals are very affordable"
  },
  {
    "start": 22.7,
    "text": "and delicious."
  },
  {
    "start": 23.7,
    "text": "I think here the food will be amazing but probably a bit more pricey than it is in"
  },
  {
    "start": 29.8,
    "text": "Seoul."
  },
  {
    "start": 30.8,
    "text": "Let's go check it out."
  },
  {
    "start": 31.8,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "start": 32.8,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "start": 33.8,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "start": 34.8,
    "text": "I do have space for two."
  },
  {
    "start": 36.8,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 37.8,
    "text": "Just as I head up, it's just my door."
  },
  {
    "start": 40.8,
    "text": "Is that going to be okay?"
  },
  {
    "start": 41.8,
    "text": "That's totally fine."
  },
  {
    "start": 42.8,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 43.8,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 44.8,
    "text": "We'll go again one two."
  },
  {
    "start": 45.8,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 46.8,
    "text": "Do you have any allergies?"
  },
  {
    "start": 47.8,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "start": 48.8,
    "text": "Anything to drink?"
  },
  {
    "start": 49.8,
    "text": "No, I think we're all set."
  },
  {
    "start": 50.8,
    "text": "We can go each."
  },
  {
    "start": 51.8,
    "text": "Yes, please."
  },
  {
    "start": 52.8,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 53.8,
    "text": "You've got bodhichang."
  },
  {
    "start": 55.8,
    "text": "Barley tea."
  },
  {
    "start": 56.8,
    "text": "I love it."
  },
  {
    "start": 57.8,
    "text": "It's perfect because it's so cold outside."
  },
  {
    "start": 59.6,
    "text": "This is nice and warm."
  },
  {
    "start": 61.0,
    "text": "Even the cups are like in Korea."
  },
  {
    "start": 66.6,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "start": 67.6,
    "text": "Thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "start": 75.6,
    "text": "We just got our food and they put it on this massive platter."
  },
  {
    "start": 80.1,
    "text": "We've got rice, soup, our main dish and seven different side dishes and looking at"
  },
  {
    "start": 87.9,
    "text": "the side dishes."
  },
  {
    "start": 88.9,
    "text": "They give you really good stuff."
  },
  {
    "start": 90.9,
    "text": "We've got fresh salmon."
  },
  {
    "start": 91.9,
    "text": "We've got some jjong."
  },
  {
    "start": 93.9,
    "text": "Like they have at solar or chusok in Korea."
  },
  {
    "start": 97.9,
    "text": "It all looks really delicious."
  },
  {
    "start": 99.7,
    "text": "And actually, I really love the interior of the restaurant."
  },
  {
    "start": 103.1,
    "text": "It reminds me of retro soul."
  },
  {
    "start": 105.4,
    "text": "So I feel like I'm in jjongno or urjido right now."
  },
  {
    "start": 108.9,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "start": 109.9,
    "text": "Let's dig in."
  },
  {
    "start": 110.9,
    "text": "Gotta start with the bun chun first, of course."
  },
  {
    "start": 112.9,
    "text": "Mmm."
  },
  {
    "start": 113.9,
    "text": "I think it's perillishy radish."
  },
  {
    "start": 116.7,
    "text": "It's just like something I've had in Seoul for sure."
  },
  {
    "start": 119.2,
    "text": "What is this?"
  },
  {
    "start": 120.2,
    "text": "Squid?"
  },
  {
    "start": 121.2,
    "text": "Maybe?"
  },
  {
    "start": 122.2,
    "text": "I'm not huge on squid."
  },
  {
    "start": 124.2,
    "text": "Mmm."
  },
  {
    "start": 125.2,
    "text": "Not bad."
  },
  {
    "start": 126.2,
    "text": "Kimchi."
  },
  {
    "start": 127.2,
    "text": "I know I love."
  },
  {
    "start": 128.2,
    "text": "I always love kimchi."
  },
  {
    "start": 130.2,
    "text": "Mmm."
  },
  {
    "start": 131.2,
    "text": "That's some good kimchi."
  },
  {
    "start": 132.2,
    "text": "Very tangy."
  },
  {
    "start": 133.2,
    "text": "Actually, I haven't had Korean food for quite some time."
  },
  {
    "start": 137.4,
    "text": "So it's really nice getting to have Korean food again."
  },
  {
    "start": 140.8,
    "text": "I ordered Chewuk for my main."
  },
  {
    "start": 143.4,
    "text": "I heard it's a popular dish here."
  },
  {
    "start": 146.6,
    "text": "This is actually so good."
  },
  {
    "start": 148.0,
    "text": "Very authentic."
  },
  {
    "start": 151.4,
    "text": "Ta-kangjang chicken."
  },
  {
    "start": 152.7,
    "text": "It's amazing that they give this as a side dish."
  },
  {
    "start": 155.7,
    "text": "Mmm."
  },
  {
    "start": 156.7,
    "text": "This is like a so-toe kangjang level."
  },
  {
    "start": 159.4,
    "text": "Soft, tender, warm marinade."
  },
  {
    "start": 162.1,
    "text": "Finally, get to try a real Korean fried chicken again."
  },
  {
    "start": 165.6,
    "text": "The thing I like about the side dishes in Seoul though,"
  },
  {
    "start": 168.2,
    "text": "is that the refills are unlimited."
  },
  {
    "start": 170.8,
    "text": "Here, I don't think it's the same."
  },
  {
    "start": 173.8,
    "text": "This is my favorite kind of bulgogi."
  },
  {
    "start": 175.5,
    "text": "This tastes really good, smoky flavor."
  },
  {
    "start": 178.1,
    "text": "I think the best option would be to get to come"
  },
  {
    "start": 181.2,
    "text": "and then one tail and one bulgogi."
  },
  {
    "start": 183.3,
    "text": "But I think I would choose bulgogi over tail."
  },
  {
    "start": 186.0,
    "text": "It's a toss-up."
  },
  {
    "start": 187.2,
    "text": "I like the bulgogi and the cheese."
  },
  {
    "start": 189.2,
    "text": "Gotta get em both."
  },
  {
    "start": 190.3,
    "text": "Thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "start": 194.0,
    "text": "Amazing, very happy."
  },
  {
    "start": 199.4,
    "text": "She wanted to have a clear day."
  },
  {
    "start": 202.7,
    "text": "It was so good."
  },
  {
    "start": 203.8,
    "text": "I noticed a lot of Koreans coming here, actually."
  },
  {
    "start": 206.6,
    "text": "That's how you know it's a good spot."
  },
  {
    "start": 208.8,
    "text": "Also, I had to laugh."
  },
  {
    "start": 210.4,
    "text": "It was kind of funny seeing Americans eating Korean food"
  },
  {
    "start": 214.6,
    "text": "and packing up the leftovers."
  },
  {
    "start": 217.1,
    "text": "I love it because I hate wasting food."
  },
  {
    "start": 220.0,
    "text": "But living in Seoul, I never see people"
  },
  {
    "start": 223.0,
    "text": "packing up bunchun to take home."
  },
  {
    "start": 225.3,
    "text": "So it kind of made me laugh."
  },
  {
    "start": 226.7,
    "text": "Can we get the bill, please?"
  },
  {
    "start": 228.1,
    "text": "Okay, thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 229.3,
    "text": "Yeah, $2 to refill your side dishes."
  },
  {
    "start": 232.6,
    "text": "If you refill your side dishes, it's got to be the chicken"
  },
  {
    "start": 235.4,
    "text": "or the salmon to be worth it."
  },
  {
    "start": 237.2,
    "text": "It's a tip."
  },
  {
    "start": 238.0,
    "text": "Tip."
  },
  {
    "start": 238.9,
    "text": "Okay, thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "start": 240.4,
    "text": "I care about tip."
  },
  {
    "start": 241.4,
    "text": "Yeah, no problem."
  },
  {
    "start": 244.5,
    "text": "You guys get busy, hey."
  },
  {
    "start": 245.8,
    "text": "Yeah, that's good though."
  },
  {
    "start": 247.3,
    "text": "That's cool."
  },
  {
    "start": 248.1,
    "text": "After tax, it's about $70."
  },
  {
    "start": 251.0,
    "text": "But we haven't paid the tip yet, either."
  },
  {
    "start": 253.3,
    "text": "So it kind of hurts my heart a little bit."
  },
  {
    "start": 255.5,
    "text": "Knowing how much I'd pay for this in Seoul,"
  },
  {
    "start": 257.9,
    "text": "it's about three times more expensive, at least."
  },
  {
    "start": 261.2,
    "text": "But for New York City standards,"
  },
  {
    "start": 263.6,
    "text": "I think it's pretty fair."
  },
  {
    "start": 265.3,
    "text": "It hurts."
  },
  {
    "start": 266.5,
    "text": "But I do love this restaurant."
  },
  {
    "start": 268.1,
    "text": "If you're in New York, I think it's worth it."
  },
  {
    "start": 269.9,
    "text": "Plus they give you free coffee."
  },
  {
    "start": 271.7,
    "text": "Coffee is included, so that's also a plus."
  },
  {
    "start": 274.9,
    "text": "Even better, mixed coffee."
  },
  {
    "start": 280.3,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "start": 286.8,
    "text": "Wow, so sweet."
  },
  {
    "start": 288.6,
    "text": "I love it."
  },
  {
    "start": 289.7,
    "text": "Perfect way to end the meal."
  },
  {
    "start": 291.4,
    "text": "We came to Marinay for lunch,"
  },
  {
    "start": 294.0,
    "text": "which is a Korean fusion restaurant"
  },
  {
    "start": 296.8,
    "text": "that specializes in hand rolls."
  },
  {
    "start": 299.5,
    "text": "It's a more casual sister restaurant to Marin,"
  },
  {
    "start": 303.6,
    "text": "which is a Michelin star restaurant here in New York City."
  },
  {
    "start": 307.5,
    "text": "Let's go check it out."
  },
  {
    "start": 320.7,
    "text": "Is the rice beer mackerel."
  },
  {
    "start": 323.4,
    "text": "OK, we'll get one of those, please."
  },
  {
    "start": 325.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 326.1,
    "text": "We're starting the afternoon off with some mackerel."
  },
  {
    "start": 330.2,
    "text": "I'm really surprised to see this in New York."
  },
  {
    "start": 333.0,
    "text": "When I lived here before, I saw soju,"
  },
  {
    "start": 335.6,
    "text": "a lot on different menus, but not mackerel."
  },
  {
    "start": 338.2,
    "text": "So maybe it's getting more popular these days in the US."
  },
  {
    "start": 342.2,
    "text": "Cheers."
  },
  {
    "start": 347.4,
    "text": "I've missed this."
  },
  {
    "start": 348.8,
    "text": "Mokkeolli is my favorite Korean alcohol."
  },
  {
    "start": 353.2,
    "text": "Our first dish is shrimp tempura,"
  },
  {
    "start": 356.2,
    "text": "and it's served with wasabi aioli."
  },
  {
    "start": 359.3,
    "text": "I think this is going to pair perfectly with our mokkeolli."
  },
  {
    "start": 363.1,
    "text": "Wow, the shrimp is so juicy inside,"
  },
  {
    "start": 366.3,
    "text": "and I love the sauce."
  },
  {
    "start": 368.0,
    "text": "I thought fried shrimp was a simple dish,"
  },
  {
    "start": 370.8,
    "text": "but the flavors are quite complex."
  },
  {
    "start": 373.2,
    "text": "Very good."
  },
  {
    "start": 374.4,
    "text": "I'll take 100 of these."
  },
  {
    "start": 375.7,
    "text": "It's a little light."
  },
  {
    "start": 376.6,
    "text": "It's a little light."
  },
  {
    "start": 378.5,
    "text": "It's very similar."
  },
  {
    "start": 380.6,
    "text": "You're saying it tastes like jocheon chicken,"
  },
  {
    "start": 382.4,
    "text": "but in the shrimp form?"
  },
  {
    "start": 383.9,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "start": 384.9,
    "text": "I can see it."
  },
  {
    "start": 385.6,
    "text": "That's fair."
  },
  {
    "start": 386.4,
    "text": "Can't go wrong with this combo."
  },
  {
    "start": 388.0,
    "text": "Can't go wrong."
  },
  {
    "start": 388.8,
    "text": "We demolish this in two seconds."
  },
  {
    "start": 391.3,
    "text": "It's so good."
  },
  {
    "start": 392.7,
    "text": "Maybe we're getting one from the mokkeolli."
  },
  {
    "start": 395.3,
    "text": "I just had to take my jacket off."
  },
  {
    "start": 396.9,
    "text": "I'm rolling up my sleeves for this."
  },
  {
    "start": 409.5,
    "text": "So the waiter recommended just eating the fatty tuna roll"
  },
  {
    "start": 413.2,
    "text": "as is because he said it has a very clean taste."
  },
  {
    "start": 416.7,
    "text": "So I'm just going to take a bite without any sauce."
  },
  {
    "start": 423.4,
    "text": "I can see what he means."
  },
  {
    "start": 425.2,
    "text": "The texture's good."
  },
  {
    "start": 426.3,
    "text": "It's not super fishy or overpowering."
  },
  {
    "start": 429.4,
    "text": "Really nice."
  },
  {
    "start": 430.2,
    "text": "And I like that the seaweed is still very crispy"
  },
  {
    "start": 433.8,
    "text": "and crunchy since it's fresh."
  },
  {
    "start": 435.4,
    "text": "I'm going to try it with some sauce"
  },
  {
    "start": 437.0,
    "text": "because he said all the sauces are house made."
  },
  {
    "start": 439.8,
    "text": "I love that they put it in squeeze bottles."
  },
  {
    "start": 441.9,
    "text": "It makes it much easier."
  },
  {
    "start": 445.3,
    "text": "I like it with the sauce."
  },
  {
    "start": 447.2,
    "text": "Very nice."
  },
  {
    "start": 448.0,
    "text": "Try the vegan one."
  },
  {
    "start": 449.2,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "start": 449.7,
    "text": "Surprisingly, I like this one more than..."
  },
  {
    "start": 452.1,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "start": 453.2,
    "text": "You like the vegan one more than the tuna?"
  },
  {
    "start": 455.2,
    "text": "This one."
  },
  {
    "start": 456.0,
    "text": "I like the tuna one more than the vegan."
  },
  {
    "start": 459.2,
    "text": "Who are we?"
  },
  {
    "start": 462.2,
    "text": "Salmon."
  },
  {
    "start": 463.2,
    "text": "Salmon."
  },
  {
    "start": 464.2,
    "text": "Salmon."
  },
  {
    "start": 465.2,
    "text": "Salmon."
  },
  {
    "start": 466.2,
    "text": "Salmon."
  },
  {
    "start": 467.2,
    "text": "I love that they give you ginger as the palate cleanser too."
  },
  {
    "start": 470.6,
    "text": "It's normal thing though."
  },
  {
    "start": 471.6,
    "text": "I feel like I love better than I expected."
  },
  {
    "start": 474.5,
    "text": "Is this one to bother you here?"
  },
  {
    "start": 476.3,
    "text": "It's on us."
  },
  {
    "start": 477.3,
    "text": "Ok."
  },
  {
    "start": 478.3,
    "text": "I just don't want to be in your way."
  },
  {
    "start": 482.3,
    "text": "You guys have a favor?"
  },
  {
    "start": 484.2,
    "text": "I like the last one, the spicy tuna."
  },
  {
    "start": 486.7,
    "text": "Oh my gosh."
  },
  {
    "start": 487.7,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "start": 488.7,
    "text": "I was like potato and a roll like that."
  },
  {
    "start": 490.7,
    "text": "I've never heard of that."
  },
  {
    "start": 491.7,
    "text": "But I really thought I was super picky with fish."
  },
  {
    "start": 494.8,
    "text": "But I loved all of the fish ones."
  },
  {
    "start": 497.1,
    "text": "Yeah, they were great."
  },
  {
    "start": 498.1,
    "text": "So I think maybe I wasn't eating like good quality fish or something."
  },
  {
    "start": 501.2,
    "text": "But this was amazing."
  },
  {
    "start": 502.2,
    "text": "Enjoyed all of it."
  },
  {
    "start": 503.2,
    "text": "It will be in just like a few minutes."
  },
  {
    "start": 505.8,
    "text": "Ok."
  },
  {
    "start": 506.8,
    "text": "Ok."
  },
  {
    "start": 507.8,
    "text": "Sounds good."
  },
  {
    "start": 508.8,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "start": 513.8,
    "text": "We also got janshu pork stew."
  },
  {
    "start": 516.2,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "start": 517.2,
    "text": "I'm back in Kuliano."
  },
  {
    "start": 519.2,
    "text": "It's transported me."
  },
  {
    "start": 521.2,
    "text": "Box of soul."
  },
  {
    "start": 522.2,
    "text": "Hmm."
  },
  {
    "start": 523.2,
    "text": "Put it similar."
  },
  {
    "start": 524.2,
    "text": "Mmm."
  },
  {
    "start": 525.2,
    "text": "Mmm."
  },
  {
    "start": 526.2,
    "text": "It's pretty good."
  },
  {
    "start": 527.2,
    "text": "Mmm."
  },
  {
    "start": 528.2,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "start": 529.2,
    "text": "This is why I can't share with you."
  },
  {
    "start": 530.2,
    "text": "It can't be done in one bite."
  },
  {
    "start": 532.2,
    "text": "Just because you can, doesn't mean you should."
  },
  {
    "start": 535.2,
    "text": "Not in sleep in the noodles."
  },
  {
    "start": 537.2,
    "text": "Just watching."
  },
  {
    "start": 540.9,
    "text": "Now we're at Don Don K BBQ."
  },
  {
    "start": 544.4,
    "text": "If you ask any American about Korean food, BBQ is probably the first thing that comes"
  },
  {
    "start": 550.8,
    "text": "to their mind."
  },
  {
    "start": 551.9,
    "text": "It has become so popular in the US, and I'm ready to eat some sun-getsal."
  },
  {
    "start": 557.2,
    "text": "Let's go."
  },
  {
    "start": 558.2,
    "text": "I have a reservation."
  },
  {
    "start": 560.5,
    "text": "What's your name on it?"
  },
  {
    "start": 562.5,
    "text": "Kali Anderson."
  },
  {
    "start": 563.5,
    "text": "The people?"
  },
  {
    "start": 564.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 565.5,
    "text": "How are you guys?"
  },
  {
    "start": 567.5,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 568.5,
    "text": "You're welcome."
  },
  {
    "start": 569.5,
    "text": "I'll give you a minute, right?"
  },
  {
    "start": 570.5,
    "text": "Thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "start": 571.5,
    "text": "You're welcome."
  },
  {
    "start": 572.5,
    "text": "Do you have any food allergies?"
  },
  {
    "start": 573.5,
    "text": "Nope."
  },
  {
    "start": 574.5,
    "text": "You guys want to start off with beer?"
  },
  {
    "start": 575.5,
    "text": "We have Don Don beer."
  },
  {
    "start": 576.5,
    "text": "Sure."
  },
  {
    "start": 577.5,
    "text": "Maybe a bottle is so dry."
  },
  {
    "start": 579.5,
    "text": "We also have our in-house Don Don beer."
  },
  {
    "start": 581.5,
    "text": "Oh, okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 582.5,
    "text": "Awesome."
  },
  {
    "start": 583.5,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 584.5,
    "text": "Here."
  },
  {
    "start": 585.5,
    "text": "Tomec."
  },
  {
    "start": 586.5,
    "text": "We have our puffer and the sausage."
  },
  {
    "start": 588.5,
    "text": "We have a new roll, general, Chinese, and chopped."
  },
  {
    "start": 592.5,
    "text": "What do you like?"
  },
  {
    "start": 593.5,
    "text": "I would say general."
  },
  {
    "start": 594.5,
    "text": "Sounds good."
  },
  {
    "start": 595.5,
    "text": "And for the choice of stews."
  },
  {
    "start": 596.5,
    "text": "Uh-huh."
  },
  {
    "start": 598.5,
    "text": "Kimchi."
  },
  {
    "start": 599.5,
    "text": "Kimchi sounds good."
  },
  {
    "start": 600.5,
    "text": "Yep."
  },
  {
    "start": 601.5,
    "text": "It's going to be our condiments."
  },
  {
    "start": 602.5,
    "text": "This is going to be our raw sabi and our sambi."
  },
  {
    "start": 604.5,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 605.5,
    "text": "So I'm going to boil it and gochujang."
  },
  {
    "start": 606.5,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 607.5,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "start": 608.5,
    "text": "I feel like I'm back in Seoul."
  },
  {
    "start": 610.5,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 621.5,
    "text": "Nice."
  },
  {
    "start": 628.5,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "start": 629.5,
    "text": "He said this is the jowl."
  },
  {
    "start": 631.5,
    "text": "I'll dip it in the salt."
  },
  {
    "start": 633.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 634.5,
    "text": "I like this one because it's not a super fatty part of meat."
  },
  {
    "start": 637.5,
    "text": "I like it a little bit chewier."
  },
  {
    "start": 639.5,
    "text": "Moxa is my favorite, so that will be the true test."
  },
  {
    "start": 644.5,
    "text": "So nice."
  },
  {
    "start": 645.5,
    "text": "Try it with a little bit of a hint of what's on me."
  },
  {
    "start": 647.5,
    "text": "I can tell you're a professional at this."
  },
  {
    "start": 649.5,
    "text": "You're a good griller."
  },
  {
    "start": 653.5,
    "text": "I'm taking his recommendation."
  },
  {
    "start": 655.5,
    "text": "Eating with the what'sabi."
  },
  {
    "start": 660.5,
    "text": "Fire."
  },
  {
    "start": 661.5,
    "text": "When I'm in the US, I really miss Korean soup."
  },
  {
    "start": 663.5,
    "text": "And this is legit."
  },
  {
    "start": 664.5,
    "text": "Here it goes."
  },
  {
    "start": 665.5,
    "text": "My favorite."
  },
  {
    "start": 669.5,
    "text": "He knows what he's doing on the grill."
  },
  {
    "start": 671.5,
    "text": "I'll tell you that much."
  },
  {
    "start": 672.5,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "start": 673.5,
    "text": "It's perfect with a little bit of what'sabi, a little bit of salt."
  },
  {
    "start": 675.5,
    "text": "I can't tell the difference."
  },
  {
    "start": 677.5,
    "text": "From when I was in Jeju trying barbecue for the first time."
  },
  {
    "start": 680.5,
    "text": "This is awesome."
  },
  {
    "start": 681.5,
    "text": "Cheers."
  },
  {
    "start": 683.5,
    "text": "Let's learn some English at Korean barbecue."
  },
  {
    "start": 687.5,
    "text": "Get on gym is egg to play."
  },
  {
    "start": 690.5,
    "text": "Some is lettuce wrap."
  },
  {
    "start": 692.5,
    "text": "Kimchi is kimchi."
  },
  {
    "start": 695.5,
    "text": "I love eating with my hand."
  },
  {
    "start": 697.5,
    "text": "Roll it up and stuff it in your face."
  },
  {
    "start": 702.5,
    "text": "Time for a Korean drinking game."
  },
  {
    "start": 704.5,
    "text": "I suck at this game now."
  },
  {
    "start": 706.5,
    "text": "I'm so bad at flicking my fingers."
  },
  {
    "start": 710.5,
    "text": "That was a good one."
  },
  {
    "start": 712.5,
    "text": "I'm going to use all my power here."
  },
  {
    "start": 716.5,
    "text": "I think my husband took it easy on me this time."
  },
  {
    "start": 720.5,
    "text": "I think he wanted an excuse to drink."
  },
  {
    "start": 724.5,
    "text": "For the sugar ice cream or sugar cream."
  },
  {
    "start": 727.5,
    "text": "Awesome."
  },
  {
    "start": 728.5,
    "text": "Thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "start": 729.5,
    "text": "I don't think I've ever had ice cream at Korean barbecue in Seoul."
  },
  {
    "start": 733.5,
    "text": "Koreans, I love your barbecue but you gotta get on that."
  },
  {
    "start": 738.5,
    "text": "This is a good touch."
  },
  {
    "start": 740.5,
    "text": "Please make sure to subscribe to our channel."
  },
  {
    "start": 743.5,
    "text": "Check out the pinned comment below."
  },
  {
    "start": 745.5,
    "text": "And I will see you all next time."
  },
  {
    "start": 747.5,
    "text": "Goodbye everybody."
  },
  {
    "start": 748.5,
    "text": "Bye bye."
  }
]